This paper deals with the use of OpenStreetMap data for driving environment understanding, which involves computer vision, machine learning, robotics, and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.CL (Computation and Language).
